Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========正文========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.53,0:00:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳…妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.89,0:00:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說這位…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是直哉先生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫塔原明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 簡單的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 想回一趟人界？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西忘記帶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 該怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把女兒帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直 直哉先生 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經有孩子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是那時的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到是需要留宿的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話 希望可以把她帶來一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為是妹妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 確實後宮搜索條件中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有加入「無小孩」這一條呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在NG掉直哉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會把公主殿下好不容易萌生的感情幼苗給掐斷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過世界樹之門能不能順利打開就不知道了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果您也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界樹之門很順利的打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想和公主殿下成為好朋友…什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來我們年紀也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年紀？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幾歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10歲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉先生是23歲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太 太不知廉恥了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個野蠻人 變態
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 不要再出現在我面…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:01:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳明明一點都不瞭解爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要血口噴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 明日葉

Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙可是我的玩具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:03:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻…可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 您還醒著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天還要早起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說的稍微過分了點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種口氣也難怪他女兒會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能立刻承認自身的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蘿黛大人的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要在這裡工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被說成那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算待遇再好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太同意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉 妳看下面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為那些花澆水的是公主殿下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從不間斷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下雖然有時有點愛生氣 不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但本性是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望明日葉可以跟公主殿下好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 爸爸的笑容真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我會再和公主殿下談一次的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我驚~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒穿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為啊因為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣又通風又舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有勒緊感 對身體也有好處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把替換用的內褲拿出來穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下已經出門了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 我還想著今天一定要搞好關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 公主殿下是去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是王族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了將來能治理好國家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解平民的生活也是十分重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是先代國王的教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過公主殿下自身是否會歌頌現在的校園生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有點微妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的學校是怎麼樣的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校庭大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有泳池嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有午餐吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想去這裡的學校呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行啊 明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去學校就能立刻見到公主殿下喔 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也不是常說吵架不宜把時間拖的太長嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去啦 想去跟公主殿下聊聊天啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉小妹妹 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三圍報來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 各位坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我來介紹一下新來的新同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫塔原明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:08:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別轉學生塔原明日葉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要好好和她相處…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有課本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借~我~看~呼~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊喵哇~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論如何都好想和公主殿下聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就到這裡來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算您是亞斯塔蘿黛殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課時也請不要講話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害妳被罵啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上學時不要嬉戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主是要有威嚴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威嚴？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是同班的蜜絲特倫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是優柏可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫琉卡 請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能由我們帶妳參觀學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳走太快了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校真的好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還有動物園 太意外了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是在教室裡和公主殿下關係很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉和公主殿下很熟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們也才剛剛認識沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為我爸爸的工作原因 我們住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼樣的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是叫做後宮的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後…後宮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是說明日葉是公主殿下的千金呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等等 這也太獵奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個年齡就能有後代 不愧是殿下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說算算年齡就不對勁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後宮是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們和公主殿下不是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道這些的話 不如直接去問她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從春季入學以來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有想過要搞好關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但想想畢竟身分懸殊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連搭個話也誠惶誠恐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一直感覺架子很大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實看上去虛榮心有點重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比較難搭話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不如今天和公主殿下一起吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後促膝長談如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事心動不如行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直猶豫不決是不會有開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把公主殿下帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起吃午飯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個精神的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在辦公室聽說大新聞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類到學校來了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現公主殿下囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼知道我在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的尾巴很招搖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:13:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨…昨天抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 妳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫明日葉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔原明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡搞完了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要和大家一起吃午飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是爸爸親手做的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還加了我最愛的筑前煮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有乾蘿蔔絲和…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西我才不想要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉也和其他的男人一樣厚顏無恥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才討厭男…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到自己的家人被這樣說會很傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下也有自己重視的家人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人有花一樣的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿黛也有像牛奶一樣甜香柔美的味道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果母親大人被人貶低我也會很難受的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下終於肯看著我講話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去找大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們聽說那個傳聞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說學校裡有人類男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是什麼樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些怕 不過還是很感興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說人類是滿身毛的四腳動物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人跟琉卡說是脖子有三米長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可聽說是齙牙直眼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不太可能做朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕快通知明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去找明日葉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真好啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能對自己那麼坦誠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我嫉妒過妳兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次是聽說妳是直哉的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟那傢伙是我的…玩具…什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到妳很快就得到了我待在這裡半年都沒有得到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我嫉妒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事實上為這樣的自己羞愧不已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是坦誠地說出來了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去就夠了 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下也在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學 學校裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說有人類的男人混進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸 爸爸來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來做什麼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來接我的話也太早了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能感覺到有什麼在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來 明日葉醬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 爸爸變得毛絨絨的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下請退後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:16:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下就由我們來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的人類 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只是肚子餓了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 公主殿下 明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把便當帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個全身是毛的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不是人類男人 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是動物園的新品種
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是天大的誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次去看看牠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得…得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這裡可是男士禁入的女校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 到入口的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被剛才那個東西一直追趕著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等反應過來的時候已經在學園裡迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就聽到明日葉的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 給我便當
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉真是個好動的孩子呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 這個是公主殿下的份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道您喜歡吃些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以做了跟明日葉一樣的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次請把公主殿下的喜好告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 爸爸的手藝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 跟大家一起吃會更美味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才各位出手相救十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是下次請別再做出那麼危險的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳們這樣有身分的人出了什麼意外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於將來的政治有莫大的損失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我必須跟特定的國家以及身分的人好好相處…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 為什麼考慮那種麻煩的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟政治什麼的沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 關鍵時刻朋友之間相互幫助是理所當然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 作為和好的證明 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啾！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是塔原流「我已經不生氣了~」之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一般是親額頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就特別服務一下親在嘴旁邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉紅透了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好刺激啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剛才叫我明日葉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我以後也直接叫名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉卡也這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿黛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿黛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿黛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿黛殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿黛笑了 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉 吃飯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至直哉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P.S. 炸肉丸我還不算討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.33,0:23:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是像以前那樣忙碌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.98,0:23:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她喜歡的新刊發售了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買…買給她的話 她會高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
